---
layout: base.njk
title: Услуги
description: Всички услуги в мрежа
pagination:
    data: services
    size: 1000
    alias: allServices
---

<section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-evergreen">Услуги</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-primary-deepsea max-w-3xl">Разгледайте всички услуги.</p>
        </div>

        <div class=" p-4 sm:p-0 sm:bg-transparent sm:shadow-none sm:rounded-none pt-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 justify-items-center">
                {% for service in allServices %}
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-md p-4 md:p-6 w-full max-w-[280px]">
                    <div
                        class="h-40 w-full rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"
                        style="background-color: {{ service.serviceCardColor or '#F5F5F5' }};"
                    >
                        {% if service.serviceIcon %}
                            <img
                                src="{{ service.serviceIcon | url }}"
                                alt="{{ service.name }}"
                                class="h-16 w-auto object-contain"
                            >
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 flex-1">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-blue leading-snug">
                            {{ service.name }}
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-primary-deepsea leading-relaxed">
                            {{ service.description }}
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full flex justify-end">
                        <a
                            href="{{ ('/uslugi/' ~ service.slug ~ '/') | url }}"
                            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary-blue text-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200"
                        >
                            Вижте услугата
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


